tly and thoroughly.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Able to operate equipment such as forklifts, scissors lift, and other appropriate equipment.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Maintain current GMP, SQF, Food Safety practices.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Other duties as assigned.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;To perform this job successfully, an individual must be able to perform each essential duty satisfactorily. The following list that follows is representative of the knowledge, skill and/or ability required:&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3+ years of experience working as an experienced level Industrial Produc

