&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The Digital Merchandiser supports execution of Nature’s Bakery’s ecommerce presence across key retailers, ensuring our products are accurately represented and optimized online. This role focuses on maintaining high-quality content, improving search visibility, and driving digital growth through strong day-to-day execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Own &lt;strong&gt;digital shelf execution&lt;/strong&gt; across retailers, ensuring product pages are accurate, complete, and up to date&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Optimize product content (titles, images, descriptions, keywords) to improve &lt;strong&gt;search visibility and conversion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Manage item setup and content syndication across platforms (e.g., Salsify, Syndigo)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with brand, sales, and creative teams to deliver and maintain content for new items, seasonal updates, and transitions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Monitor product pages across key retailers (Amazon, Walmart, Target, Kroger, etc.) and proactively identify issues and opportunities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Analyze content performance, search trends, and competitor activity to inform improvements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Execute test-and-learns and track results to support optimization efforts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Support development of digital best practices and playbooks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1–3 years of relevant experience&lt;/strong&gt; in ecommerce, digital merchandising, or related field&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with retailer.com environments (e.g., Amazon, Walmart) and content tools (e.g., Salsify, Syndigo) preferred&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Understanding of &lt;strong&gt;SEO and digital shelf fundamentals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong attention to detail and organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities and meet deadlines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
